(1980, 1, '2015-03-24 01:05:28', '2015-03-24 01:05:28', '[full_width]\r\n\r\n[row]\r\n\r\n[video link=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTgioNkVFrE\"]\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n[parallax imgsrc=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/ogc2.jpg\"]\r\n[row][/row]\r\n[row]\r\n<h2>The Levels</h2>\r\n[/row]\r\n[row]\r\n[quarter_column]\r\n<h3>Freshmen</h3>\r\n[paragraph]BEGINNER\r\nFocus on developing style, finding and refining inner movement, and building stage presence. We also include an introduction to the business proceedings in the entertainment industry.[/paragraph]\r\n[/quarter_column]\r\n[quarter_column]\r\n<h3>Sophomore</h3>\r\n[paragraph]INTERMEDIATE\r\nHere we put their skills to the test by applying them in professional environments. At this level we force students to expand their comfort zone and diversify their dance vocabulary.[/paragraph]\r\n[/quarter_column]\r\n[quarter_column]\r\n<h3>GC</h3>\r\n[paragraph]ADVANCED\r\nAt this level, students learn to be artists by refining their performance skills. Here they also begin developing leadership skills. This is the most elite level of the company, and students may be chosen to perform in company bookings.[/paragraph][/quarter_column]\r\n[quarter_column]\r\n<h3>OGC</h3>\r\n[paragraph]EXPERT\r\nThe Original members of The Girls Club. These women are the core Venue Entertainment Performers. Having worked closely with Tamina over the years, they are now strong leaders in all levels of the company.[/paragraph][/quarter_column]\r\n[/row]\r\n[row][/row]\r\n[row][/row]\r\n[/parallax]\r\n\r\n[row class=\"whatItTakes\"]\r\n<h1>Have what it takes?</h1>\r\n<span class=\"btnHolder\">\r\n[button id=\"academyButton\" link=\"https://thegirlsclub.typeform.com/to/c937Hp\"]<span style=\"color:#111111;\">Fill Out an Application</span>[/button]\r\n</span>\r\n[/row]\r\n[row class=\"whatItTakes\"][/row]\r\n[/full_width]', 'Academy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1846-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-03-24 01:05:28', '2015-03-24 01:05