(2025, 1, '2016-01-08 21:22:22', '2016-01-08 21:22:22', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Tamina Pollack-Paris is an emerging choreographer drawing inspiration from classic and modern influences. Adaptability and professionalism are what creates our one-of-a-kind experience. Tamina has worked with artists such as Lady Gaga, Justin Bieber, Aloe Blacc, and Ke$ha. Her TV career includes roles in The Next Step, Degrassi, Glee, American Idol, X-Factor, and a top 16 contestant on Canada\'s \'So You Think You Can Dance: Season 1\'. Tamina is always training and pushing herself to the limit, so she can help dancers around the world to create their own path to success.', 'Tamina Pollack-Paris', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1737-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-01-08 21:22:22', '2016-01-08 21:22:22', '', 1737, 'http://testgirls/1737-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
