(2096, 1, '2015-05-18 14:07:47', '2015-05-18 14:07:47', '<a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/bevhotel_v7-girls-complete.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2128\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/bevhotel_v7-girls-complete.jpg\" alt=\"BEV | The Woman Behind the Icon\" width=\"612\" height=\"792\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>The Girls Club</strong> presents, <strong><em>BEV</em></strong>: The Woman Behind the Icon. Join us at The Beverley Hotel as we take you through moments in history, highlighting underrated iconic women that have revolutionized music, art, dance and fashion in their eras. The Girls Club will unveil their stories through live, immersive exhibits for art lovers of all walks of life.\r\n\r\nThe night will begin with the soothing sounds of our talented DJs, infused with innovative, thought provoking performances. We will then lead you through the wonderful rooms at The Beverley Hotel where you will experience our live exhibits.\r\n\r\nFollowing the show, you will have the choice of 2 backdrops: The Sultry lounge with the soothing flow of an upscale house party, or the breathtaking patio featuring the dazzling sounds of Studio 54 and live entertainment.\r\n\r\nDrink, Eat, and Dance the night away.\r\nThe party ends at the stroke of midnight.\r\n\r\nIt’s your night, choose your own adventure.\r\n\r\n<strong>2 VIEWINGS</strong>\r\n- 1st Heat: Doors at 6pm. Show at 6:30pm\r\n- 2nd Heat: Doors at 7:30pm. Show at 8pm\r\n\r\n<strong>MUSIC BY</strong>: <a href=\"https://flyladydi.wordpress.com\" target=\"_blank\"> DJ Fly Lady Di </a>\r\n\r\n<strong>FASHIONS CREATED BY</strong>: <a href=\"http://www.somkong.ca\" target=\"_blank\">Som Kong</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>VINTAGE FASHIONS PROVIDED BY</strong>: <a href=\"http://www.torontovintagesociety.ca\" target=\"_blank\">The Toronto Vintage Society</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>JEWELRY BY</strong>: <a href=\"http://shopforjayu.com\" target=\"_blank\">Shop For Jayu</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>HAIR BY</strong>: <a href=\"http://www.jazma.com\" target=\"_blank\">Jazma Hair Inc.</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>MAKE UP BY</strong>: <a href=\"http://www.jl-th.net\" target=\"_blank\">Julie Thai</a>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n***<strong>SPECIAL GUEST PERFORMER</strong>***\r\nToronto\'s most talented Drag Diva\r\nMiss <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tynomi.banks?fref=ts\">Tynomi Banks</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tynomi.banks?fref=ts\"><img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/TB-small.jpg\" alt=\"Tynomi Banks\" /></a>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTICKETS\r\n\r\n$30 in Advance\r\n$35 at the Door\r\n\r\nTickets can be purchased at:\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%; text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"260\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"auto\" marginheight=\"5\" marginwidth=\"5\" src=\"//eventbrite.ca/tickets-external?eid=17035312077&amp;ref=etckt\"></iframe>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 10px; padding: 5px 0 5px; margin: 2px; width: 100%; text-align: left;\"><a class=\"powered-by-eb\" style=\"color: #dddddd; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.eventbrite.ca/r/etckt\" target=\"_blank\">Powered by Eventbrite</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\nLimited Capacity. So please buy your tickets early to avoid disappointment.', 'BEV', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bev', '', '', '2015-06-25 04:26:08', '2015-06-25 04:26:08', '', 0, 'http://testgirls/?page_id=2096', 0, 'page', '', 0),
