(2137, 1, '2015-06-05 02:12:18', '2015-06-05 02:12:18', '<img src=\"https://scontent-ord1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xft1/t31.0-8/11334209_370791279776953_5146746634292242096_o.jpg\" alt=\"WORKSHOP/AUDITION FLYER\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>THE ULTIMATE WORKSHOP EXPERIENCE\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nYOU are your greatest asset! It\'s not always about straight choreo in this industry- if you don\'t understand your body, how to walk, how to groove, and how to simply sell yourself as a performer you\'re missing some of your most valuable fundamentals. \r\n\r\nJOIN US as we take you through a full day of some of the MOST USEFUL skills you can hone as a dancer and performance artist!!\r\n\r\nDATE: Sunday June 14th\r\nWHERE: The Citadel. 304 Parliament St. Toronto, ON \r\nTIME: 11:30-3pm\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>Part 1:</ul>\r\n11:30-11:45 Yoga w. Lisa Clarke.\r\n11:45-12:15 Heels Technique w. Tamina Pollack-Paris\r\n12:15-1 Performance 101 w. Monica Gold \r\n1-1:15 Break\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul>Part 2:</ul>\r\n1:15-2 Grooves w. Amanda-May Wilson\r\n2:00-3 Audition 101 w. Tamina Pollack-Paris\r\n\r\nEARLY BIRD PRICE : $50 for full day / $30 for half day\r\nDAY OF PRICE: $60 for full day / $40 for half day\r\n\r\nFor inquiries or sign ups please email/e-transfer: info@thegirlsclub.ca\r\n\r\nHeels suggested but not mandatory ! \r\n\r\nALSO, Our Academy will be holding auditions on JUNE 20th from 1-3:30pm\r\nALL LEVELS WELCOMED\r\nBring your drive, dedication, headshots and resumes!\r\nFor more information on our Academy, click <a href=\"http://www.thegirlsclub.ca/academy\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/367821616750436/\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook Event Info</a>\r\n\r\nLOOKING FORWARD TO SEEING YOU AND WATCHING YOU GROW AS A FULL PACKAGE PERFORMER!\r\n\r\nXo \r\nThe Girls Club', 'WORKSHOP SERIES & ACADEMY AUDITIONS!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-girls-club-fundamental-workshop-series-academy-auditions', '', '\nhttp://www.thegirlsclub.ca/academy', '20