Y</strong>: <a href=\"http://www.jazma.com\" target=\"_blank\">Jazma Hair Inc.</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>MAKE UP BY</strong>: <a href=\"http://www.jl-th.net\" target=\"_blank\">Julie Thai</a>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n***<strong>SPECIAL GUEST PERFORMER</strong>***\r\nToronto\'s most talented Drag Diva\r\nMiss <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tynomi.banks?fref=ts\">Tynomi Banks</a>\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tynomi.banks?fref=ts\"><img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/TB-small.jpg\" alt=\"Tynomi Banks\" /></a>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTICKETS\r\n\r\n$30 in Advance\r\n$35 at the Door\r\n\r\nTickets can be purchased at:\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%; text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n<iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"260\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"auto\" marginheight=\"5\" marginwidth=\"5\" src=\"//eventbrite.ca/tickets-external?eid=17035312077&amp;ref=etckt\"></iframe>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 10px; padding: 5px 0 5px; margin: 2px; width: 100%; text-align: left;\"><a class=\"powered-by-eb\" style=\"color: #dddddd; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.eventbrite.ca/r/etckt\" target=\"_blank\">Powered by Eventbrite</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\nLimited Capacity. So please buy your tickets early to avoid disappointment.', 'BEV', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2096-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-25 04:26:08', '2015-06-25 04:26:08', '', 2096, 'http://testgirls/2096-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
