(2258, 1, '2015-12-28 19:48:45', '2015-12-28 19:48:45', '<a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-28-at-2.46.41-PM.png\"><img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-28-at-2.46.41-PM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-12-28 at 2.46.41 PM\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1120\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2260\" /></a>\r\n\r\nToronto!\r\nCome burn off all those holiday goodies at the \"Sweat the Season\" Dance Workshop, January 7th @The Gladstone Hotel!\r\n\r\nEver wonder how a first impression is made? Here’s your chance to learn valuable confidence building skills that are transferable in many areas of life, whether in a social setting or a job interview. Learn ways to stay physically fit, and have fun doing it!  All levels welcomed! Class will be taught at a beginner level, in a very open and supportive environment.\r\n\r\nThis beginner level class, taught by GC creative director Tamina Pollack-Paris, will provide tricks to building a daily routine to become a healthier, happier YOU.\r\nHot new dance moves! \r\nBody conditioning and confidence building exercises!\r\nGoal and intention setting!\r\nSTART YOUR NEW YEAR RIGHT!!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/sweat-the-season-dance-class-for-beginners-tickets-20075036976\" target=\"_blank\">Click here for more information, or to register!</a>\r\n\r\nBring your sneakers and your goals and aspirations for 2016! :)', '\"Sweat the Season\" Dance Workshop with TAMINA |  January 7th!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sweat-the-season-dance-workshop-with-tamina-january-7th', '', '', '2015-12-28 19:56:25', '2015-12-28 19:56:25', '', 0, 'http://testgirls/?p=2258', 0, 'post', '', 0),
