(2305, 0, '2016-01-28 13:11:56', '2016-01-28 13:11:56', '', '12568821_814665041989686_2101040163_n', 'We are pleased to announce that The Girls Club will be partnering with RMT Chris Delos Reyes! \nSpecial rates will be offered to students enrolled in our Academy. \nChris Delos Reyes is a Registered Massage Therapist with a background as a Professional Dancer and a Fitness Instructor. He has been practicing as an RMT for 5 years and has led a successful clientele base within sports medicine clinics in Toronto. He has travelled with his practice on the trans-continental VIA Rail Train across Canada and has recently arrived back from Los Angeles treating hundreds of fitness enthusiasts at the worlds biggest fitness expedition, The LA Fit Expo 2016. \nAuditions for The Girls Club Academy will be held this Sunday from 10am-1pm @ Dancemakers studio. Pre-registration required.\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/events/1794148870812574/\n\n#thegirlsclub  #dance #toronto #stayready #RMT #academyauditions', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12568821_814665041989686_2101040163_n', '', '', '2016-01-28 13:11:56', '2016-01-28 13:11:56', '', 0, 'http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/12568821_814665041989686_2101040163_n.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
