(2308, 1, '2016-03-23 23:50:02', '2016-03-23 23:50:02', '<a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/GC-Greatest-Hits-show-flyerV4.jpg\"><img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/GC-Greatest-Hits-show-flyerV4.jpg\" alt=\"ENCORE\" width=\"3300\" height=\"2550\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2310\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>The Girls Club</strong> presents: <strong><em>ENCORE</em></strong>\r\n\r\nThe Girls Club is back with our first ever full length Stage show! \"Encore\" revisits our crowd favorites and debuts fresh new numbers performed by all levels of The Girls Club Academy.\r\n\r\nJoin us as we explore the musical genius of iconic artists revamped in a fresh and exciting way. Witness the characters we create and the personas we embody in our 90 minute homage to the old and new.\r\n\r\nThe Girls Club is renowned for transforming environments into an experience. For one night only, step into our world of movement, intention, passion and ambition. \r\n\r\nThe event will be hosted by one of Toronto’s top Drag performers, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tynomi.banks/?fref=ts\" target=\"_blank\">Tynomi Banks</a>.\r\n\r\nDoors 7PM\r\nShow 7:30PM\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>TICKETS</strong>\r\n\r\n$15 Early Bird\r\n$20 After April 12th\r\n\r\nTickets can be purchased at:\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%; text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\" ><iframe  src=\"//eventbrite.ca/tickets-external?eid=23317348818&ref=etckt\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"260\" width=\"100%\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" marginheight=\"5\" marginwidth=\"5\" scrolling=\"auto\" allowtransparency=\"true\"></iframe><div style=\"font-family:Helvetica, Arial; font-size:10px; padding:5px 0 5px; margin:2px; width:100%; text-align:left;\" ><a class=\"powered-by-eb\" style=\"color: #dddddd; text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.eventbrite.ca/r/etckt\">Powered by Eventbrite</a></div></div>\r\n\r\nLimited Capacity. So please buy your tickets early to avoid disappointment.\r\n\r\n\r\nPrizes will be provided by our wonderful sponsor <a href=\"http://paitoronto.com\" target=\"_blank\">PAI, Northern Thai Kitchen</a>\r\n\r\nFor more information, check out our website www.thegirlsclub.ca or contact us at info@thegirlsclub.ca\r\n\r\n__________________\r\n\r\nAbout The Girls Club:\r\n\r\nTHE FUTURE OF VENUE ENTERTAINMENT\r\n\r\nTHE GIRLS CLUB is a collective of some of the most talented entertainers in the city. As a unit, we thrive on creating remarkable experiences through live performance arts. Our spontaneous & immersive performances are centered around your audience and tailor-made to the needs of your event. We create an alternate reality through character development, music selection, props, utilization of the venue, and world class dance routines. We can woo any audience in a private venue, public event, live exhibit, or corporate function.\r\n\r\nThe Girls Club Academy is geared towards the development and empowerment of tomorrow’s top female performers. Our students earn industry level dance training and business leadership skills through a specialized curriculum that provides the necessary skill set to thrive in any professional environment.\r\n\r\nOur Programs: Beginner series, Freshmen, Sophomore & Professional \r\n\r\n\r\nTAMINA POLLACK-PARIS \r\nFounder | Executive Director\r\nCREATIVE , INNOVATIVE, DETAIL ORIENTED\r\nIn 2013 Tamina Pollack-Paris founded The Girls Club with a clear vision and direction. Now, as an established collective, we provide audiences with a spontaneous and unforgettable show every time we take the stage.\r\n\r\nTamina has worked with artists such as Lady Gaga, Justin Bieber, Aloe Blacc, and Ke$ha. Her TV career includes roles in The Next Step, The Stanley Dynamic, Degrassi, Glee, American Idol, X-Factor, and Canada’s ‘So You Think You Can Dance: Season 1.\r\n\r\nSustaining a career in both Canadian and US markets, Tamina continues to be a powerful talent in whichever milieu she finds herself in.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n------------------------\r\nFacebook: thegirlsclub.ca\r\nInstagram: @the_girlsclub\r\nTwitter: @the_girlsclub\r\n', 'ENCORE', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'encore', '', '', '2016-03-23 23:53:27', '2016-03-23 23:53:27', '', 0, 'http://testgirls/?page_id=2308', 0, 'page', '', 0),
