(2326, 1, '2016-07-01 20:41:50', '2016-07-01 20:41:50', '<a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/TGC-Drop-in-Classes.jpg\"><img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/TGC-Drop-in-Classes.jpg\" alt=\"TGC Drop in Classes\" width=\"1638\" height=\"1257\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2320\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe Girls Club is opening our doors to invite you to come and dance with us this summer!\r\n\r\nLearn confidence building activities, while staying fit and dancing to your favourite hit tracks! \r\n\r\nNo experience necessary, just bring positive vibes and get ready to have fun and sweat!\r\n\r\nWorkshop Dates:\r\nJuly 9th: One Dance - Drake\r\nJuly 23rd: Into you - Ariana Grande\r\n\r\n2:00-3:30pm at Gotta Dance Studios. 3581 Dundas st. W\r\n\r\n$45 +HST for 2 classes\r\n$25 +HST for 1 class\r\n\r\nEmail: info@thegirlsclub.ca to register.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to dancing with you this summer!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/259116817801471/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/259116817801471/</a>', 'Drop in Beginner Classes!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2321-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-01 20:41:50', '2016-07-01 20:41:50', '', 2321, 'http://testgirls/2321-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
