(2329, 1, '2016-08-13 23:12:39', '2016-08-13 23:12:39', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Girls Club Presents, \"The Stay Ready Series\".</p><p>This 2-Day, 5-Hour intensive is designed for any dancer (male or female) seeking well rounded professional level training to gear up for the upcoming season. Styles covered range from fundamental performance techniques, to Krump, Salsa, House and gymnastic tricks to use in audition environments.</p><p>Staying ready means doing anything you can as a performer to broaden your dance horizons by welcoming many diverse disciplines into your vocabulary.</p><p>\"If you stay ready, you ain\'t gotta get ready\"</p><p>Let\'s get ready together,</p><p>xo The Girls Club</p>', 'Stay Ready Workshop Series', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'stay-ready-workshop-series', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:48:25', '2018-01-19 09:48:25', '', 0, 'http://testgirls/?p=2329', 0, 'post', '', 0),
