(2342, 1, '2016-12-17 21:12:44', '2016-12-17 21:12:44', '<p>CALLING ALL PROFESSIONAL and INTERMEDIATE level performers seeking a supportive, driven and empowering collective to grow as individuals and artists!</p><p>The Girls Club will be holding auditions for all levels of our Academy. This program is for the ambitious individual looking for industry level dance and business training.</p><p>Learn proper heels technique, while working on stage presence and confidence building techniques. Explore your artistic potential with the opportunity to apply them in professional settings!</p><p>Where: Winchester St Theatre<br /> When: January 3rd 2017 6-8pm<br /> Cost: Free</p><p>Bring your headshots, resumes and a winning attittude!</p><p>Start the new year off right by taking steps to achieve your goals and become your best self!</p><p>For more information, email us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@thegirlsclub.ca\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@thegirlsclub.ca</a></p><p>Facebook event <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1151551438272343/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HERE</a><br /> ------</p><p><a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2341\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook.jpg\" alt=\"girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook\" width=\"3200\" height=\"3488\" /></a></p><p>Want a taste of what happens in a GC Academy rehearsal?<br /> The Girls Club is excited to announce our first Open Class!<br /> Come and experience what it is like to train with The Girls Club Academy for a day for free. That’s right, there is no cost, it’s FREE.<br /> This class is open to all levels. Bring yourself, your heels, a positive attitude and water (you’ll need it 😉).</p><p>Looking forward to dancing with you in 2017!<br /> -The Girls Club<br /> #StayReady #Dontbeafraidofheights #strongertogether</p>', 'GC ACADEMY 2017 AUDITIONS + Open Classes!!!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gc-academy-2017-auditions-open-classes', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:46:31', '2018-01-19 09:46:31', '', 0, 'http://testgirls/?p=2342', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(2343, 1, '2016-12-17 21:11:32', '2016-12-17 21:11:32', '<a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-auditions-2017-Facebook.jpg\"><img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-auditions-2017-Facebook.jpg\" alt=\"girls-club-academy-auditions-2017-facebook\" width=\"3200\" height=\"3488\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2340\" /></a>\r\nCALLING ALL PROFESSIONAL and INTERMEDIATE level performers seeking a supportive, driven and empowering collective to grow as individuals and artists!\r\n\r\nThe Girls Club will be holding auditions for all levels of our Academy. This program is for the ambitious individual looking for industry level dance and business training.\r\n\r\nLearn proper heels technique, while working on stage presence and confidence building techniques. Explore your artistic potential with the opportunity to apply them in professional settings! \r\n\r\n\r\nWhere: Winchester St Theatre\r\nWhen: January 3rd 2017 6-8pm\r\nCost: Free\r\n\r\nBring your headshots, resumes and a winning attittude!\r\n\r\nStart the new year off right by taking steps to achieve your goals and become your best self!\r\n\r\nFor more information, email us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@thegirlsclub.ca\" target=\"_blank\">info@thegirlsclub.ca</a>\r\n\r\nFacebook event <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1151551438272343/\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a>\r\n------\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook.jpg\"><img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook.jpg\" alt=\"girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook\" width=\"3200\" height=\"3488\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2341\" /></a>\r\n\r\nWant a taste of what happens in a GC Academy rehearsal?\r\nThe Girls Club is excited to announce our first Open Class!\r\nCome and experience what it is like to train with The Girls Club Academy for a day for free. That’s right, there is no cost, it’s FREE.\r\nThis class is open to all levels. Bring yourself, your heels, a positive attitude and water (you’ll need it 😉).\r\n\r\nLooking forward to dancing with you in 2017!\r\n-The Girls Club\r\n#StayReady #Dontbeafraidofheights #strongertogether\r\n', 'GC ACADEMY 2017 AUDITIONS + Open Classes!!!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2342-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-17 21:11:32', '2016-12-17 21:11:32', '', 2342, 'http://testgirls/2342-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
