(2383, 1, '2017-04-29 20:43:10', '2017-04-29 20:43:10', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>New at The Girls Club!<br /> Beginners, check off your Calendars for a Monthly Date with us!<br /> On the last tuesday of every month from 7-8:30PM we will now be offering beginner classes! Stay tuned for the monthly schedule and class themes!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Our next session:<span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><br /> -May 29th @ 7PM<br /> -Winchester St. Theatre<br /> -Price: $15<br /> -Theme: Stay Tuned <span class=\"_47e3 _5mfr\" title=\"wink emoticon\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v8/ff6/2/16/1f609.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">;)</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div class=\"text_exposed_show\"><p>What Students can expect:<br /> -An all inclusive, safe environment where students can learn all the amazing confidence building techniques we teach at The Girls Club, at a beginner level!<br /> -Experience the emotional and physical benefits of movement therapy<br /> -Simple exercises to stay fit &amp; healthy<br /> -Most importantly, awesome new moves to show off at your next party!</p><p>Bring your dancing shoes and get ready to groove <span class=\"_47e3 _5mfr\" title=\"wink emoticon\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v8/ff6/2/16/1f609.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">;)</span></span></p><p>Email info@thegirlsclub.ca to register!</p></div>', 'Beginner\'s Class May 29th!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'beginners-class-may-29th', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:43:29', '2018-01-19 09:43:29', '', 0, 'http://testgirls/?p=2383', 0, 'post', '', 0),
