(2425, 2, '2018-01-19 09:43:29', '2018-01-19 09:43:29', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>New at The Girls Club!<br /> Beginners, check off your Calendars for a Monthly Date with us!<br /> On the last tuesday of every month from 7-8:30PM we will now be offering beginner classes! Stay tuned for the monthly schedule and class themes!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Our next session:<span class=\"text_exposed_show\"><br /> -May 29th @ 7PM<br /> -Winchester St. Theatre<br /> -Price: $15<br /> -Theme: Stay Tuned <span class=\"_47e3 _5mfr\" title=\"wink emoticon\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v8/ff6/2/16/1f609.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">;)</span></span></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div class=\"text_exposed_show\"><p>What Students can expect:<br /> -An all inclusive, safe environment where students can learn all the amazing confidence building techniques we teach at The Girls Club, at a beginner level!<br /> -Experience the emotional and physical benefits of movement therapy<br /> -Simple exercises to stay fit &amp; healthy<br /> -Most importantly, awesome new moves to show off at your next party!</p><p>Bring your dancing shoes and get ready to groove <span class=\"_47e3 _5mfr\" title=\"wink emoticon\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v8/ff6/2/16/1f609.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /><span class=\"_7oe\">;)</span></span></p><p>Email info@thegirlsclub.ca to register!</p></div>', 'Beginner\'s Class May 29th!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2383-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:43:29', '2018-01-19 09:43:29', '', 2383, 'http://testgirls/2383-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2426, 2, '2018-01-19 09:44:07', '2018-01-19 09:44:07', '<p>Looking for a fun way to celebrate Mother\'s day? Join The Girls Club for their annual Mother/Daughter day dance class!<br /> Lots of Beyonce, Laughs and Goodies provided by @the_crystal_kitchen. Don\'t miss it!</p><p>Email: info@thegirlsclub.ca to register <span class=\"_47e3 _5mfr\" title=\"smile emoticon\"><img class=\"img\" src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v8/feb/2/16/1f642.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></p>', 'Annual Mother\'s Day Class May 14th!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2380-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:44:07', '2018-01-19 09:44:07', '', 2380, 'http://testgirls/2380-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2427, 2, '2018-01-19 09:45:08', '2018-01-19 09:45:08', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>The Girls Club Academy Auditions are May 8th!</strong></span></p><p>Learn to dance confidently in your own skin!</p><p>Experience the benefits of movement therapy and the power of unity in an all-inclusive and safe environment. Our program is geared to push students outside of their comfort zones to realize their true creative potentials.</p><p>Learn proper heels technique, while working on stage presence through confidence building exercises and  artist development.</p><p>Along with training in various genres, Students will also have the opportunity to:<br /> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Work professionally<br /> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Perform in Showcases<br /> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Film concept videos<br /> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Shoot with Professional Photographers<br /> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Explore Spiritual growth<br /> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Be Mentored by an Industry Professional<br /> Join a sisterhood of like-minded women<br /> + so much more!</span></p><p>Levels:<br /> Beginner monthly classes (email to register)<br /> Freshman (Intermediate)<br /> Sophomore (Advanced)<br /> GC Professional<br /> Bring your heels and get ready to groove ;)</p><p>For more information on our programs feel free to email us at info@thegirlsclub.ca<br /> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/280664015712156/\">https://www.facebook.com/events/280664015712156/</a></p><p>Sincerely,<br /> The Girls Club xo</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'The Girls Club Academy Auditions Spring/Summer 2017', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2376-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:45:08', '2018-01-19 09:45:08', '', 2376, 'http://testgirls/2376-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2428, 2, '2018-01-19 09:46:28', '2018-01-19 09:46:28', '<p>CALLING ALL PROFESSIONAL and INTERMEDIATE level performers seeking a supportive, driven and empowering collective to grow as individuals and artists!</p><p>The Girls Club will be holding auditions for all levels of our Academy. This program is for the ambitious individual looking for industry level dance and business training.</p><p>Learn proper heels technique, while working on stage presence and confidence building techniques. Explore your artistic potential with the opportunity to apply them in professional settings!</p><p>Where: Winchester St Theatre<br /> When: January 3rd 2017 6-8pm<br /> Cost: Free</p><p>Bring your headshots, resumes and a winning attittude!</p><p>Start the new year off right by taking steps to achieve your goals and become your best self!</p><p>For more information, email us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@thegirlsclub.ca\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@thegirlsclub.ca</a></p><p>Facebook event <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1151551438272343/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HERE</a><br /> ------</p><p><a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2341\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook.jpg\" alt=\"girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook\" width=\"3200\" height=\"3488\" /></a></p><p>Want a taste of what happens in a GC Academy rehearsal?<br /> The Girls Club is excited to announce our first Open Class!<br /> Come and experience what it is like to train with The Girls Club Academy for a day for free. That’s right, there is no cost, it’s FREE.<br /> This class is open to all levels. Bring yourself, your heels, a positive attitude and water (you’ll need it 😉).</p><p>Looking forward to dancing with you in 2017!<br /> -The Girls Club<br /> #StayReady #Dontbeafraidofheights #strongertogether</p>', 'GC ACADEMY 2017 AUDITIONS + Open Classes!!!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2342-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:46:28', '2018-01-19 09:46:28', '', 2342, 'http://testgirls/2342-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2429, 2, '2018-01-19 09:46:31', '2018-01-19 09:46:31', '<p>CALLING ALL PROFESSIONAL and INTERMEDIATE level performers seeking a supportive, driven and empowering collective to grow as individuals and artists!</p><p>The Girls Club will be holding auditions for all levels of our Academy. This program is for the ambitious individual looking for industry level dance and business training.</p><p>Learn proper heels technique, while working on stage presence and confidence building techniques. Explore your artistic potential with the opportunity to apply them in professional settings!</p><p>Where: Winchester St Theatre<br /> When: January 3rd 2017 6-8pm<br /> Cost: Free</p><p>Bring your headshots, resumes and a winning attittude!</p><p>Start the new year off right by taking steps to achieve your goals and become your best self!</p><p>For more information, email us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@thegirlsclub.ca\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">info@thegirlsclub.ca</a></p><p>Facebook event <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1151551438272343/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HERE</a><br /> ------</p><p><a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2341\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook.jpg\" alt=\"girls-club-academy-open-class-facebook\" width=\"3200\" height=\"3488\" /></a></p><p>Want a taste of what happens in a GC Academy rehearsal?<br /> The Girls Club is excited to announce our first Open Class!<br /> Come and experience what it is like to train with The Girls Club Academy for a day for free. That’s right, there is no cost, it’s FREE.<br /> This class is open to all levels. Bring yourself, your heels, a positive attitude and water (you’ll need it 😉).</p><p>Looking forward to dancing with you in 2017!<br /> -The Girls Club<br /> #StayReady #Dontbeafraidofheights #strongertogether</p>', 'GC ACADEMY 2017 AUDITIONS + Open Classes!!!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2342-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:46:31', '2018-01-19 09:46:31', '', 2342, 'http://testgirls/2342-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2430, 2, '2018-01-19 09:47:31', '2018-01-19 09:47:31', '<p>***Tis the season Toronto!***</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Girls Club Academy is opening its doors and welcomes you for a very special Christmas class. In this Christmas themed beginner class you will go through confidence building exercises and choreography while dancing to all your favourite Christmas songs!<br /> Start your holiday season off right with this fun, energetic class! Santa will be sure to add you on his nice list, or naughty ;)</p><p>DATE: December 19th 2016<br /> ADDRESS: Winchester Street Theatre (80 Winchester St. Toronto, ON.)<br /> TIME: 7:00-8:30 PM<br /> COST: $15 if you pre-register.<br /> $20 after Dec. 8th.</p><p>Email: info@thegirlsclub.ca to register<br /> FB Event: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/1278241358907315/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://www.facebook.com/events/1278241358907315</a></p><p>Hope to dance with you soon!</p>', 'Christmas Themed Beginner Class December 19th!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2334-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:47:31', '2018-01-19 09:47:31', '', 2334, 'http://testgirls/2334-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2431, 2, '2018-01-19 09:48:25', '2018-01-19 09:48:25', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Girls Club Presents, \"The Stay Ready Series\".</p><p>This 2-Day, 5-Hour intensive is designed for any dancer (male or female) seeking well rounded professional level training to gear up for the upcoming season. Styles covered range from fundamental performance techniques, to Krump, Salsa, House and gymnastic tricks to use in audition environments.</p><p>Staying ready means doing anything you can as a performer to broaden your dance horizons by welcoming many diverse disciplines into your vocabulary.</p><p>\"If you stay ready, you ain\'t gotta get ready\"</p><p>Let\'s get ready together,</p><p>xo The Girls Club</p>', 'Stay Ready Workshop Series', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2329-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-19 09:48:25', '2018-01-19 09:48:25', '', 2329, 'http://testgirls/2329-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
