 size=\"1/2\" class=\"program-text-column\"]</p><p>[header][paragraph class=\"program-header\"]OUR PROGRAM[/paragraph][/header]</p><p>[header][paragraph class=\"program-underheader\"]CONFIDENCE FROM THE INSIDE-OUT[/paragraph][/header]</p><p>[header][paragraph class=\"program-small-yellow-header\"]What Students can expect:[/paragraph][/header]</p><p>[su_list icon=\"icon: circle\" class=\"program-big-list\"]</p><ul><li>Heels Technique, Hip Hop, Jazz, Artist Development/stage presence coaching + more! !</li><li>Confidence Building &amp; Leadership Exercises</li><li>Mentorship Circles !</li><li>Movement Therapy through Intuitive Feels Sessions</li><li>Exploration of Spiritual Growth</li><li>Showcases &amp; Paid Opportunities + so much more!</li></ul><p>[/su_list]</p><p>[header][paragraph class=\"program-small-yellow-header\"]Membership Options:[/paragraph][/header]</p><p>[su_list icon=\"icon: none\" class=\"program-small-list\"]</p><ul><li>3 Months $120+HST</li><li>6+ Months $100+HST</li></ul><p>[/su_list]</p><p>[/su_column]</p><p>[su_column size=\"1/4\" class=\"program-third-column\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-2502\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/new3-300x300.png\" alt=\"new3\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />[/su_column]</p><p>[/parallax]</p><p>========================</p></div><p>[row]</p><p>[video link=\"https://vimeo.com/131172841\"]</p><p>[/row]<br /> [row]<br /> [paragraph]</p><ul>The Girls Club</ul><p>is a distinguished Academy geared towards the development and empowerment of tomorrow’s top female performers. Our students earn industry level dance training and business leadership skills through a specialized curriculum that provides the necessary skill set to thrive in any professional environment. We teach our students valuable audition techniques to transform their passion into a career with success &amp; longevity. The Academy’s culture identifies with strong, passionate, and elegant leaders. <strong>Excellence</strong> is our expectation, along with <strong>focus</strong>, <strong>ambition</strong> and <strong>teamwork</strong>. Our hand-picked team represents the finest multi-disciplinary group of professional artists.  </p><ul>Four distinct programs</ul><p>inspire and sustain dancers through training, exclusive access, mentorship and career opportunities. Founded over two and a half years ago, the Academy has already produced a diverse demographic of talented, intelligent women who are ready to take the industry by storm.</p><p><a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/GIRLSCLUB-Academy.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Our Academy Brochure</a></p><p>[/paragraph]<br />[/row]</p><p>============================</p><p>[row class=\"whatItTakes\"]</p><h3>See What We\'re Up To</h3><p><span class=\".btnHolder\"><br /> [button link=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/NowYouCanSitWithUs\"]<img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/youtube.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>[/button]<br /> <span class=\".btnHolder\">[button link=\"https://twitter.com/The_GirlsClub/\"]<img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/twitter.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>[/button]<br /> <span class=\".btnHolder\">[button link=\"https://instagram.com/the_girlsclub/\"]<img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/instagram.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>[/button] <span class=\".btnHolder\">[button link=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheGirlsClub.ca?ref=br_tf\"]<img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facebook.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>[/button]<br /> [/row]<br /> [row class=\"whatItTakes\"]</p><h1>Have what it takes?</h1><p><span class=\"btnHolder\"><br /> [button id=\"academyButton\" link=\"https://thegirlsclub.typeform.com/to/c937Hp\"]<span style=\"color: #111111;\">Fill Out an Application</span>[/button]<br /> </span><br /> [/row]<br /> [row class=\"whatItTakes\"][/row]<br /> [/full_width]</p>', 'Academy Attempt', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2574-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-0