alignnone size-full wp-image-2438\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/workshop1.jpg\" alt=\"workshop1\" width=\"356\" height=\"634\" /></p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-header\"]Beginners Heels Saturday’s at 2PM[/paragraph] </p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-text\"]- safe space to explore your femininity and embrace all the qualities that make you, YOU! Step into our playground, and step into your power!</p><p>Class highlights: getting to know your body, simple workouts to stay fit, learning how to strut confidently in your heels and tapping into your inner Goddess with a fun dance routine!</p><p>*no dance experience required*[/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-item-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2441\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/workshop2.jpg\" alt=\"workshop2\" width=\"356\" height=\"634\" /></p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-header\"]Intermediate Heels Thursdays at 8PM[/paragraph] </p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-text\"]Get a taste of The Girls Club academy! Class components: Heels technique, performance tips and musically inspired combos that focus on strengthening a weekly area of development.</p><p>This is a great space for dancers who are looking to expand their talents beyond choreography retention to step into their greatest potential as performers.[/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-item-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2442\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/workshop3.jpg\" alt=\"workshop3\" width=\"356\" height=\"634\" /></p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-header\"]Intuitive Feels Fridays at 11AM[/paragraph] </p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-text\"]Body &amp; Soul connection for dancers. This class is designed to create a safe space for free and authentic expression. Students will learn how to tune into their intuitions to embody the language of the soul through movement. Searching within establishes the foundation for a genuine emotional connection with your audience. Dancing from the inside-out!</p><p>Class structure: Active meditations, connection exercises, grounding grooves &amp; free form movement. [/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row]</p><div class=\"her-story-section-wrapper\"><p>[header class=\"her-story-header\"][paragraph]HER STORY [/paragraph][/header]</p><p>[slide-anything id=\'2548\']</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[full_width]</p></div></div></div></div><p>[row]</p><p>[video link=\"https://vimeo.com/131172841\"]</p><p>[/row]<br /> [row]<br /> [paragraph]</p><ul>The Girls Club</ul><p>is a distinguished Academy geared towards the development and empowerment of tomorrow’s top female performers. Our students earn industry level dance training and business leadership skills through a specialized curriculum that provides the necessary skill set to thrive in any professional environment. We teach our students valuable audition techniques to transform their passion into a career with success &amp; longevity. The Academy’s culture identifies with strong, passionate, and elegant leaders. <strong>Excellence</strong> is our expectation, along with <strong>focus</strong>, <strong>ambition</strong> and <strong>teamwork</strong>. Our hand-picked team represents the finest multi-disciplinary group of professional artists.  </p><ul>Four distinct programs</ul><p>inspire and sustain dancers through training, exclusive access, mentorship and career opportunities. Founded over two and a half years ago, the Academy ha