column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-header\"]Intuitive Feels Fridays at 11AM[/paragraph] </p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-text\"]Body &amp; Soul connection for dancers. This class is designed to create a safe space for free and authentic expression. Students will learn how to tune into their intuitions to embody the language of the soul through movement. Searching within establishes the foundation for a genuine emotional connection with your audience. Dancing from the inside-out!</p><p>Class structure: Active meditations, connection exercises, grounding grooves &amp; free form movement. [/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</div>[/full_width]', 'Academy in Process', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2574-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-23 08:45:48', '2018-01-23 08:45:48', '', 2574, 'http://testgirls/2574-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
