ge-2417\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/mentor1.jpg\" alt=\"mentor\" width=\"600\" height=\"924\" /></p><p>[paragraph class=\"mentor-name\"]<strong>TAMINA POLLACK-PARIS</strong>[/paragraph]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"mentor-occupation\"]<em>Founder &amp; Executive Director</em>[/paragraph]</p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\" class = \"mentor-text\"]</p><p>[paragraph]<strong>Tamina Pollack-Paris</strong> – an entrepreneur, performer and global inspiration! She is the founder of The Girls Club, a distinguished dance academy in Toronto that empowers tomorrows’ top performers through an integrated performance and business curriculum. Her flare and attention to detail are qualities that are instilled into the nature of the academy.[/paragraph]</p><p>[paragraph]Tamina has worked with artists such as Lady Gaga, Justin Bieber, Aloe Blacc, and Ke$ha. Her TV career includes roles in The Next Step, The Stanley Dynamic, Degrassi, Glee, American Idol, X-Factor, and a Canada’s ‘So You Think You Can Dance: Season 1. [/paragraph]</p><p>[paragraph]Tamina is always training and pushing herself to the limit, so she can help dancers around the world to create their own path to success.[/paragraph]</p><p>[paragraph]<strong>“Stay ready, so you never have to get ready.”</strong>[/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column][/row]</div>[/full_width]\r\n[full_width]<div class=\"workshops-section-wrapper\"><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-header-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p>[header class=\"workshops-header\"]<strong>WORKSHOPS</strong>[/header]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshops-underheader\"]<strong>upcoming classes!</strong>[/paragraph]</p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-item-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2438\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/workshop1.jpg\" alt=\"workshop1\" width=\"356\" height=\"634\" /></p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-header\"]Beginners Heels Saturday’s at 2PM[/paragraph] </p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-text\"]- safe space to explore your femininity and embrace all the qualities that make you, YOU! Step into our playground, and step into your power!</p><p>Class highlights: getting to know your body, simple workouts to stay fit, learning how to strut confidently in your heels and tapping into your inner Goddess with a fun dance routine!</p><p>*no dance experience required*[/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-item-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2441\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/workshop2.jpg\" alt=\"workshop2\" width=\"356\" height=\"634\" /></p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-header\"]Intermediate Heels Thursdays at 8PM[/paragraph] </p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-text\"]Get a taste of The Girls Club academy! Class components: Heels technique, performance tips and musically inspired combos that focus on strengthening a weekly area of development.</p><p>This is a great space for dancers who are looking to expand their talents beyond choreography retention to step into their greatest potential as performers.[/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-item-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2442\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/workshop3.jpg\" alt=\"workshop3\" width=\"356\" height=\"634\" /></p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-header\"]Intuitive Feels Fridays at 11AM[/paragraph] </p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-text\"]Body &amp; Soul connection for dancers. This class is designed to create a safe space for free and authentic expression. Students will learn how to tune into their intuitions to embody the language of the soul through movement. Searching within establishes the foundation for a genuine emotional connection with your audience. Dancing from the inside-out!</p><p>Class structure: Active meditations, connection exercises, grounding grooves &amp; free form movement. [/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</div>[/full_width]\r\n[full_width]<div class=\"her-story-section-wrapper\">[parallax imgsrc=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/program-bg.jpg\"][header class=\"her-story-header\"][paragraph]HER STORY [/paragraph][/header][slide-anything id=\'2548\']</div>[/full_width]', 'Academy in Process', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2574-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-23 08:50:36', '2018-01-23 08:50:36', '', 2574, 'http://testgirls/2574-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
