(2620, 2, '2018-01-23 11:21:39', '2018-01-23 11:21:39', '<p>[full_width]</p><div class=\"philosophy-section-wrapper\"><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"philos-header-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"][header philos-header22]OUR PHILOSOPHY[/header]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"philos-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[half_column space=\"true\"]</p><p>[header type=\"3\" class=\"philos-underheader\"]Confidence Through Mindfulness[/header]</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">[paragraph class=\"philos-text\"]The Girls Club is a distinguished Academy designed to empower women to step into their truest and most authentic selves! Our students earn industry level dance training and valuable professional tools to transform their passion into a career with success &amp; longevity. Constructive feedback, focus, ambition and teamwork are what creates our all-inclusive and safe environment. We offer Beginner and Professional programs to inspire personal growth through training, mentorship and performance opportunities. Founded in 2013, the Academy has already produced a diverse demographic of talented, intelligent women who are leaders in their own right.[/paragraph]</p><p>[/half_column]</p><p>[half_column space=\"true\"]</p><p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2349 size-full\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/16123959_945880228881944_1535364208894410752_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"429\" /></p><p>[/half_column]</p><p>[/row]</p></div><p>[/full_width]<br /> [full_width]</p><div class=\"program-section-wrapper\"><p>[parallax imgsrc=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/program-bg.jpg\"]</p><p>[su_column size=\"1/4\" class=\"program-third-column\"]<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-2459 size-medium\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/small1-300x300.png\" alt=\"small1\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />[/su_column]</p><p>[su_column size=\"1/2\" class=\"program-text-column\"]</p><p>[header][paragraph class=\"program-header\"]OUR PROGRAM[/paragraph][/header]</p><p>[header][paragraph class=\"program-underheader\"]CONFIDENCE FROM THE INSIDE-OUT[/paragraph][/header]</p><p>[header][paragraph class=\"program-small-yellow-header\"]What Students can expect:[/paragraph][/header]</p><p>[su_list icon=\"icon: circle\" class=\"program-big-list\"]</p><ul><li>Heels Technique, Hip Hop, Jazz, Artist Development/stage presence coaching + more! !</li><li>Confidence Building &amp; Leadership Exercises</li><li>Mentorship Circles !</li><li>Movement Therapy through Intuitive Feels Sessions</li><li>Exploration of Spiritual Growth</li><li>Showcases &amp; Paid Opportunities + so much more!</li></ul><p>[/su_list]</p><p>[header][paragraph class=\"program-small-yellow-header\"]Membership Options:[/paragraph][/header]</p><p>[su_list icon=\"icon: none\" class=\"program-small-list\"]</p><ul><li>3 Months $120+HST</li><li>6+ Months $100+HST</li></ul><p>[/su_list]</p><p>[/su_column]</p><p>[su_column size=\"1/4\" class=\"program-third-column\"]<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-2502\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/new3-300x300.png\" alt=\"new3\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />[/su_column][/parallax]</p></div><p>[/full_width]<br /> [full_width]</p><div class=\"mentor-section-wrapper\"><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"mentor-header-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"][/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">[header class=\"mentor-header\"]THE WOMAN BEHIND THE CLUB[/header]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"main-mentor-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\" class = \"mentor-third-column\"]</p><p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2516\" src=\"http://thegirlsclubbyben/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/mentor.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"755\" /><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2417\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/mentor1.jpg\" alt=\"mentor\" width=\"600\" height=\"924\" /></p><p>[paragraph class=\"mentor-name\"]<strong>TAMINA POLLACK-PARIS</strong>[/paragraph]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"mentor-occupation\"]<em>Founder &amp; Executive Director</em>[/paragraph]</p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\" class = \"mentor-text\"]</p><p>[paragraph]<strong>Tamina Pollack-Paris</strong> – an entrepreneur, performer and global inspiration! She is the founder of The Girls Club, a distinguished dance academy in Toronto that empowers tomorrows’ top performers through an integrated performance and business curriculum. Her flare and attention to detail are qualities that are instilled into the nature of the academy.[/paragraph]</p><p>[paragraph]Tamina has worked with artists such as Lady Gaga, Justin Bieber, Aloe Blacc, and Ke$ha. Her TV career includes roles in The Next Step, The Stanley Dynamic, Degrassi, Glee, American Idol, X-Factor, and a Canada’s ‘So You Think You Can Dance: Season 1. [/paragraph]</p><p>[paragraph]Tamina is always training and pushing herself to the limit, so she can help dancers around the world to create their own path to success.[/paragraph]</p><p>[paragraph]<strong>“Stay ready, so you never have to get ready.”</strong>[/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column][/row]</p></div><p>[/full_width]<br /> [full_width]</p><div class=\"workshops-section-wrapper\"><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-header-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p>[header class=\"workshops-header\"]<strong>WORKSHOPS</strong>[/header]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshops-underheader\"]<strong>upcoming classes!</strong>[/paragraph]</p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-item-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2438\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/workshop1.jpg\" alt=\"workshop1\" width=\"356\" height=\"634\" /></p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-header\"]Beginners Heels Saturday’s at 2PM[/paragraph] </p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-text\"]- safe space to explore your femininity and embrace all the qualities that make you, YOU! Step into our playground, and step into your power!</p><p>Class highlights: getting to know your body, simple workouts to stay fit, learning how to strut confidently in your heels and tapping into your inner Goddess with a fun dance routine!</p><p>*no dance experience required*[/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-item-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2441\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/workshop2.jpg\" alt=\"workshop2\" width=\"356\" height=\"634\" /></p><p>[/third_column]</p><p>[two_thirds_column space=\"false\"]</p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-header\"]Intermediate Heels Thursdays at 8PM[/paragraph] </p><p>[paragraph class=\"workshop-item-text\"]Get a taste of The Girls Club academy! Class components: Heels technique, performance tips and musically inspired combos that focus on strengthening a weekly area of development.</p><p>This is a great space for dancers who are looking to expand their talents beyond choreography retention to step into their greatest potential as performers.[/paragraph]</p><p>[/two_thirds_column]</p><p>[/row]</p><p>[row headertype=\"6\" class=\"workshops-item-row\" space=\"true\" narrowcontent=\"true\"]</p><p>[third_column space=\"true\"]</p><p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-2442\" src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/workshop3.jpg\" alt=\"workshop3\" width=\"356\" height=\"634\" /></p><p>[/t