(2632, 2, '2018-01-23 15:33:24', '2018-01-23 15:33:24', '[full_width]\r\n\r\n[row]\r\n\r\n[video link=\"https://vimeo.com/131172841\"]\r\n[/row]\r\n[row]\r\n[paragraph] <ul>\r\nThe Girls Club</ul> is a distinguished Academy geared towards the development and empowerment of tomorrow’s top female performers. Our students earn industry level dance training and business leadership skills through a specialized curriculum that provides the necessary skill set to thrive in any professional environment. We teach our students valuable audition techniques to transform their passion into a career with success & longevity. The Academy’s culture identifies with strong, passionate, and elegant leaders. <strong>Excellence</strong> is our expectation, along with <strong>focus</strong>, <strong>ambition</strong> and <strong>teamwork</strong>. Our hand-picked team represents the finest multi-disciplinary group of professional artists.\r\n \r\n\r\n<ul>\r\nFour distinct programs</ul> inspire and sustain dancers through training, exclusive access, mentorship and career opportunities. Founded over two and a half years ago, the Academy has already produced a diverse demographic of talented, intelligent women who are ready to take the industry by storm.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/GIRLSCLUB-Academy.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Our Academy Brochure</a>\r\n\r\n[/paragraph]\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n[parallax imgsrc=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/ogc2.jpg\"]\r\n[row][/row]\r\n[row]\r\n<h2>The Levels</h2>\r\n[/row]\r\n[row]\r\n[quarter_column]\r\n<h3>GC Workshop Series</h3>\r\n[paragraph]BEGINNER\r\n\r\n6 week cumulative program\r\nTuition: $175.00\r\nLet your sense of femininity bloom. Learn valuable confidence building skills, ways to stay physically fit, and have fun doing it!\r\nClasses taught in a very open and supportive environment.\r\n\r\nSeries end showcase\r\n*No audition necessary. Email to register[/paragraph]\r\n[/quarter_column]\r\n[quarter_column]\r\n<h3>Freshmen</h3>\r\n[paragraph]DANCE AFTER YOUR COMPETITIVE STUDIO\r\n\r\nBridging the gap between competitive studio training and working professionally. Learn to apply skills and techniques from your home studios to work successfully in industry level environments.\r\n\r\n* Audition required [/paragraph]\r\n[/quarter_column]\r\n[quarter_column]\r\n<h3>Sophomore</h3>\r\n[paragraph]INT/ADV\r\n\r\nFocus on developing style, finding and refining inner movement, and building stage presence. We also include an introduction to entertainment business and apply them in professional environments. At this level we force students to expand their comfort zone and diversify their dance vocabulary.\r\n\r\n*Paid opportunities for members scouted to work professionally at GC\r\n*Audition Required[/paragraph][/quarter_column]\r\n[quarter_column]\r\n<h3>GC</h3>\r\n[paragraph]PROFESSIONAL\r\n\r\nThe most elite level of the company. Students learn to be artists by refining their performance and leadership skills. The Girls Club doubles as a full service venue entertainment company that creates innovative, high caliber and interactive performances in various establishments. Students at this level may be chosen to perform in company bookings.\r\n\r\n*Professional Experience &amp; Paid opportunities\r\n*Audition Required[/paragraph][/quarter_column]\r\n[/row]\r\n[row][/row]\r\n[row][/row]\r\n[/parallax]\r\n\r\n[row class=\"whatItTakes\"]\r\n<h3>See What We\'re Up To</h3>\r\n<span class=\".btnHolder\">\r\n[button link=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/NowYouCanSitWithUs\"]<img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/youtube.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>[/button]\r\n<span class=\".btnHolder\">[button link=\"https://twitter.com/The_GirlsClub/\"]<img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/twitter.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>[/button]\r\n<span class=\".btnHolder\">[button link=\"https://instagram.com/the_girlsclub/\"]<img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/instagram.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>[/button] <span class=\".btnHolder\">[button link=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheGirlsClub.ca?ref=br_tf\"]<img src=\"http://testgirls/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/facebook.png\" alt=\"\" /></span>[/button]\r\n[/row]\r\n[row class=\"whatItTakes\"]\r\n<h1>Have what it takes?</h1>\r\n<span class=\"btnHolder\">\r\n[button id=\"academyButton\" link=\"https://thegirlsclub.typeform.com/to/c937Hp\"]<span style=\"color: #111111;\">Fill Out an Application</span>[/button]\r\n</span>\r\n[/row]\r\n[row class=\"whatItTakes\"][/row]\r\n[/full_width]', 'Academy-Old-Version', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1846-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-23 15:33:24', '2018-01-23 15:33:24', '', 1846, 'http://testgirls/1846-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
